<bibRefCitation author="Ueno" box="[1172,1302,711,733]" pageId="19" pageNumber="220" refString="Ueno, S. - I. (1974) The trechid beetles of the Ryukyu Islands. Memoirs of the National Science Museum, Tokyo, (7), 157 - 167." type="journal article" year="1974">
