<number box="[1130,1183,742,764]" pageId="19" pageNumber="220" value="1873.0">1873</number>
</taxonomicName>
, due to the variability in the shape of the pronotum and the 
<collectingCountry box="[523,644,774,795]" name="Hong Kong" pageId="19" pageNumber="220">Hong Kong</collectingCountry>
